title: Does Google Earth Reveal a Sunken Ship in a Japanese Port?
subtitle: Contrary to TikTok shenanigans, the boat is neither the RMS Titanic nor the Ottoman frigate Ertuğrul that is sometimes referred to as "the Titanic of Turkey."
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Satellite imagery used in Google Earth and Google Maps reveals a sunken ship in a port on a Japanese Island.
